Kittani Warrior
The Kittani are an insectoid alien humanoid race in service to the Splugorth
of Atlantis. Kittani Warriors are their elite military class: fast, strong,
and equipped with some of the most advanced technology available on Rifts
Earth. They are among the most feared opponents of any Coalition unit.

Kittani Warriors choose from Weapons, Physical, Military, and Espionage skill
categories. They are trained in power armor operation, energy weapons, and
the particular brutality of Splugorth military doctrine.

Note: This OCC is restricted to Kittani race characters only.

Attribute requirements: None beyond race.
Starting equipment: Kittani combat power armor, Kittani laser rifle,
energy clips, combat blade, and Splugorth field rations.
